<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Retreat" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Retreat,</orth> subst. the act of retiring in war: <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.323" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 323</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.286" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 2, 286</bibl> (the earlier O. Edd. <emph>retraite</emph>). <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.8.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 8, 15</bibl> (Q <emph>retire</emph>). <cit><quote>to make r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 170</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.3.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 3, 78</bibl>. <cit><quote>to sound r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.163" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 163</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 2, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.8.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 8, 4</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>